This revision does not appear to be appreciably different from the Ax revisions.. aside from the case ('''Ax''' revs. use the ancient style casing, '''Bx''' revisions use the boxy grey + teal casing). :The OS is assumed to remain '''ThreadX''' G3.0f.3.0c on these units..
